<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.2.2">
<l>tōṭaviḻ nīlam maṇaṅko ṭukkuñ cūḻpuṉal cūḻku ṭantaik kiṭanta</l>
<l>cēṭarko leṉṟu terikka māṭṭēṉ ceñcuṭa rāḻi yuñcaṅ kumēnti</l>
<l>pāṭaka mella ṭiyārva ṇaṅkap paṉmaṇi mutto ṭilaṅku cōti</l>
<l>āṭakam pūṇṭo runāṉku tōḷu maccō voruva raḻakiyavā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I cannot tell whether he is the youth who lies in Kuṭantai</l>
<l rend="indent">encircled by circling waters</l>
<l>Where blue lilies with unfurled petals waft fragrance!</l>
<l rend="indent">[He has] four arms bearing the conch and red flaming discus,</l>
<l>Wearing gold [ornaments] with light which glitters</l>
<l rend="indent">from pearls and many jewels,</l>
<l>As devotees worship at his anklets. Oh, the way that one is handsome!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
